{"questionId":"2169400","questionHtml":"<p>A photon of wavelength <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>λ</mi></math> scatters off an electron at rest. The scattered photon has wavelength <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>λ</mi><mo>'</mo></math>.</p>\n<p>What is the fraction of the incident photon energy that gets transferred to the electron?</p>\n<p><br>A.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mi>λ</mi><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mo>'</mo></mrow></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>B.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mo>'</mo></mrow><mi>λ</mi></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>C.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>-</mo><mi>λ</mi></mrow><mi>λ</mi></mfrac></math></p>\n<p>D.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mo>'</mo><mo>-</mo><mi>λ</mi></mrow><mrow><mi>λ</mi><mo>'</mo></mrow></mfrac></math></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>D</p>","meta":{"questionId":"2169400","referenceCode":"SPM.1A.HL.TZ0.35","subjectId":"59-dp-physics-first-assessment-2025","title":"A photon of wavelength λ scatters off an electron at rest. The scattered photon has wavelength λ'. What is the fraction of the incident photon energy that gets transferred to the e","paper":"1A","level":"HL","questionNumber":"35","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["E. Nuclear and quantum physics","E. Nuclear and quantum physics","E.2 Quantum physics"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}},"schemaVersion":2}